OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cfollowing death of woman in Derbyshire
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder following the death of a
OL,8,Fwoman in South Derbyshire.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to reports that a
OL,11,Fwoman had been found with stab wounds
OL,12,Fin The Crest, in Linton, in
OL,13,FSwadlincote, just after 2.30pm on
OL,14,FSunday, 21 June.
OL,16,FA 72-year-old woman was pronounced
OL,17,Fdead at the scene. A 52-year-old man
OL,18,Fhas been arrested on suspicion of
OL,19,Fmurder and remains in police custody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
