PN,34302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782148757
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cfollowing death of woman in Derbyshire
OL,6,FPolice say the woman's family have
OL,7,Fbeen made aware and are being
OL,8,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Tony Owen, from
OL,11,Fthe East Midlands Special Operations
OL,12,FUnit, who is leading the
OL,13,Finvestigation, said: "Members of the
OL,14,Fpublic can expect to see an increased
OL,15,Fpolice presence in the area while we
OL,16,Fcarry out our enquiries.
OL,18,F"We are aware that this may cause some
OL,19,Fconcern in the community, but I would
OL,20,Flike to reassure residents that this
OL,21,Fis believed to be an isolated incident.
OL,26,@uD@VOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1782148757
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cfollowing death of woman in Derbyshire
OL,6,F"If you have any concerns or would
OL,7,Flike to pass on any information,
OL,8,Fplease feel free to approach officers."
OL,10,FAs part of the investigation, police
OL,11,Fare appealing for anyone with
OL,12,Finformation to come forward.
OL,14,FOfficers are keen to hear from anyone
OL,15,Fwith CCTV, Ring doorbell or dash cam
OL,16,Ffootage which covers The Crest between
OL,17,F12.01am on Saturday (20 June) and 3pm
OL,18,Fon Sunday (21 June).
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@gO]
